"index_reference": "4526: tree of life",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>One of two trees situated in the centre of the Garden of Eden. It is also mentioned in Revelation, where it symbolises life and salvation.</p>\n<h2>The tree of life in the Garden of Eden</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:8-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:8–2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22-Gen3:24\">GEN 3:22–3:24</a></p>\n<h2>The tree of life in Revelation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:2\">REV 22:1–22:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14-Rev22:15\">REV 22:14–22:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:18-Rev22:19\">REV 22:18–22:19</a></p>\n<h2>The tree of life as a metaphor</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:4\">PRO 15:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:18\">PRO 3:13–3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:30\">PRO 11:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:12\">PRO 13:12</a></p>",
